SUMMARY:MDS Welcome Breakfast
LOCATION:BME Commons
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a warm and spirited welcome as we celebrate the r
 eturn of our MDS colleagues to the BME community!\n\n \n\nWe’re delighted
  to have you back and look forward to reconnecting\, building new collabo
 rations\, and continuing our shared work together. \n\n \n\nBreakfast wil
 l be served as we gather informally from 10:00–11:00 AM in the BME Common
 s.\n\n \n\nWe hope you’ll stop by to say hello and help us mark this spec
 ial homecoming!\n\n \n
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
